International Society for Infectious Diseases
<http://www.isid.org/>
From: Pablo Nart <p.nart@ntlworld.com>
Date: 19 Sep 2004
Source: El Periodico, 14 Sep 2004 [in Spanish, summarized by Mod.JW, edited]
<http://www.elperiodico.com/default.asp?idpublicacio_PK=6&idioma=CAS&idnotici
